 } } \right|$$ 
<br><br>R<sub>1</sub> $$ \to $$ R<sub>1</sub> + R<sub>2</sub> + R<sub>3</sub>
<br><br>$$ = \left| {\matrix{
   {a + b + c} &amp; {a + b + c} &amp; {a + b + c}  \cr 
   {2b} &amp; {b - c - a} &amp; {2b}  \cr 
   {2c} &amp; {2c} &amp; {c - a - b}  \cr 

 } } \right|$$
<br><br>$$ = \left( {a + b + c} \right)\left| {\matrix{
   1 &amp; 0 &amp; 0  \cr 
   {2b} &amp; { - \left( {a + b + c} \right)} &amp; 0  \cr 
   {2c} &amp; {2c} &amp; {c - a - b}  \cr 

 } } \right|$$
<br><br>$$=$$ (a + b + c) (a + b + c)<sup>2</sup>
